  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for sponsorship of the Carbon Pricing in a Dynamic, Second-Best World workshop&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;This grant will support an academic conference on carbon pricing. The workshop will bring together scholars from the fields of public and environmental economics, political economy, comparative politics, innovation economics, and energy systems, alongside civil society, policy, and social movement leaders, to focus on the role carbon pricing can play and the political economy consideration that hinder its adoption. The conference will also explore alternatives to carbon pricing.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
